arStrings.szText: Casting a {c_important}Subterfuge{/c} Skill leaves behind a {c_important}Decoy Trap{/c} that continuously Taunts and lures enemies. The {c_important}Decoy Trap{/c} explodes after {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 1"]{/c} seconds dealing {c_random}[Affix_Flat_Value_1]{/c} Shadow damage. Can occur every {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0"]{/c} seconds.
